IONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nWe appreciate your response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=8237252e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"2ce33585a86d2a5e3eca3d575f7e27b1e0f639f5","tid":1396441,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"kill2#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「救人！」世紀最大救義士唯一方法 正式上線 第三波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「救人！」世紀最大救義士唯一方法 正式上線 第二波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395073\" data-auto-lin